Yogini : Admit when you feel the cool breeze in your hands?

00:14:52.178 --> 00:14:54.243
Correspondent: Cool breeze?

00:14:55.187 --> 00:14:58.958
Yogini: Breeze of the Sprit.
This is the breeze of the Sprit.

