Correspondent: Breeze of Spirit?

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:01.536
Yogini : Yes, Spirit.

00:15:01.561 --> 00:15:03.283
Correspondent:  Feels on hands?

00:15:03.325 --> 00:15:05.000
Shri Mataji: ...to the divine power.

00:15:05.128 --> 00:15:07.017
Yogini : Divine power.

00:15:16.169 --> 00:15:21.315
You can feel it at top of your head at the same time.

00:15:25.754 --> 00:15:29.216
Interviewer : Yes. I feel it very strongly.

00:15:29.973 --> 00:15:36.373
Yogini: Very strongly he feels the breeze on his head.

00:15:36.398 --> 00:15:38.604
Yogini: Very strongly he feels.

00:15:38.629 --> 00:15:42.481
Shri Mataji: This is the all-pervading power of Divine Love.

00:15:45.251 --> 00:15:48.481
Yogini : Other peoples Kundalini also can be awaken.

00:15:51.573 --> 00:15:53.731
Correspondent: Was that fast?

00:15:54.236 --> 00:15:58.943
Shri Mataji: This is the triangular bone
(showing him on the Sahaj booklet)

00:16:03.260 --> 00:16:05.444
It raises through these six centers.

00:16:08.379 --> 00:16:11.377
Ultimately it pierces this sixth center

00:16:11.409 --> 00:16:14.284
and then you felt it.

00:16:25.038 --> 00:16:29.093
Shri Mataji: You can have this and you can feel it.

