That was [taken] on a boat, on a ride.

00:17:39.453 --> 00:17:42.286
That is the day, the 5th of May it was.

00:17:47.968 --> 00:17:50.348
Shri Mataji: There were all people sitting here around Me.

00:17:57.715 --> 00:18:03.433
Shri Mataji: That was the day -long time
back – was the 5th of May 1970 –

00:18:03.458 --> 00:18:04.980
when the Sahasrara was opened

00:18:13.334 --> 00:18:15.000
in India.

00:18:20.262 --> 00:18:22.270
Shri Mataji: This  happened much later.

00:18:26.579 --> 00:18:30.061
We were in [UNCLEAR]  and we were going by boat.

00:18:30.094 --> 00:18:34.575
Shri Mataji: At that same time this photo came.

00:18:42.976 --> 00:18:44.269
Yogini: The 5th of May?

00:18:44.285 --> 00:18:48.346
Shri Mataji: Yes, [the] 5th of May.
But 10 years later.

00:19:03.790 --> 00:19:06.443
Yogini: There are a lot of people sitting around You?

00:19:06.468 --> 00:19:08.166
Shri Mataji: Yes, but you can’t see them.

00:19:08.191 --> 00:19:10.852
They have all disappeared on the sides.

00:19:16.563 --> 00:19:18.225
Shri Mataji: This is the last photograph.

00:19:18.250 --> 00:19:21.717
but there are other
which show people first

00:19:21.726 --> 00:19:23.844
and gradually they disappear.

00:19:39.635 --> 00:19:46.752
Shri Mataji: Now this is another one.
With the white saree, standing in the sea.

00:19:46.808 --> 00:19:52.624
And this light appeared in the heart,
on My heart.

00:20:08.460 --> 00:20:11.303
Shri Mataji: There are thousands of photographs,

00:20:11.320 --> 00:20:12.748
Thousands of them.

00:20:25.628 --> 00:20:31.140
Shri Mataji: My whole face was covered with the light.

00:20:31.156 --> 00:20:33.225
Very strong light

00:20:33.250 --> 00:20:37.174
But the flowers are all right there,
nothing happens to them.
